{"nodes":[{"id":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Начало","content":{"items":[{"id":"19acac9c-f447-47de-9647-f0a1c1929179","type":"image","resourcePath":"res/images/3ee3796a-4afb-4cc6-9a44-1d87bf0dfd43.png","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8d028fa4-45fb-49ba-94b2-759221c0ad5d","type":"text","text":"Вы — известный археолог, ищущий следы древнего Затерянного Города. \nВ вашем распоряжении дневник вашего предшественника, который исчез при поисках. \nСегодня вы прибываете в джунгли, где, по слухам, находится вход в город.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"092e1081-1ab2-4ae8-bd7c-631f09556ea6","type":"button","text":"исследовать джунгли","targetNodeId":"b6f42c10-cf03-45ea-9061-3b99e4b1c3f0","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e022fde4-331f-4d4c-940b-a239db8ac247","type":"button","text":"осмотреть лагерь предшественника","targetNodeId":"6098d8c9-95f5-4283-a29b-cde1081738aa","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"439655af-88ac-426a-ad1d-3eaa499651cf","type":"button","text":"спросить местных жителей","targetNodeId":"0f529608-c3fc-440d-a323-85ad9f0ef752","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":203.7035371984536,"y":14.87058644918022,"color":4281896508,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"b6f42c10-cf03-45ea-9061-3b99e4b1c3f0","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Исследовать джунгли","content":{"items":[{"id":"60bcb21d-d407-4c2b-8bf9-90e1f88cd18f","type":"text","text":"Вы углубляетесь в джунгли. \nВскоре вы находите древний камень с высеченными символами. \nКажется, это часть карты.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"8dce2319-2812-4ea8-84d1-f62d5a6c9bc9","type":"button","text":"изучить символы","targetNodeId":"d2d14f56-0bf8-4ae3-89d6-56640c3280c3","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4a968a2b-2c72-4913-bda2-3cdff6e015b7","type":"button","text":"продолжить путь","targetNodeId":"4bc1f724-adcf-46f8-a56d-4b4151165456","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-507.1023439874444,"y":-11.901105607590534,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"6098d8c9-95f5-4283-a29b-cde1081738aa","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Лагерь","content":{"items":[{"id":"207be187-65f8-4e62-9647-98cbdd1ac7da","type":"text","text":"Вы находите заброшенный лагерь. \nСреди вещей вы обнаруживаете карту с пометками и записку: '**[color=#F7A20C]Остерегайтесь Хранителей[/color].**'","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ca3fce58-5ab5-47ac-ba69-3b63a1834c8f","type":"button","text":"прочесть дневник","targetNodeId":"f7c1f27e-3c82-47f4-8c64-85a6e58c7da0","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"5315e12e-617d-4e24-bfae-f40d53dd6717","type":"button","text":"взять карту","targetNodeId":"6904963d-ba72-4e04-8f7f-95b2c5899d4c","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a494e463-236f-4d30-8b17-6fd0af30e54b","type":"button","text":"оставить лагерь","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":203.74284201387513,"y":388.0849171821064,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"0f529608-c3fc-440d-a323-85ad9f0ef752","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Спросить","content":{"items":[{"id":"721651d2-ba05-4fc8-ae2e-3bcc54a9211f","type":"text","text":"Местные жители рассказывают вам о древних легендах. \nОни говорят, что город охраняют духи, и только достойный может войти.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"bcb0591b-90bf-40ef-b9dc-9d9f751dbd96","type":"button","text":"попросить проводника","targetNodeId":"48d780f2-18aa-4b0e-aed6-10ae2072d52d","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"94a741eb-a632-4216-a9d1-eddd2b56ea82","type":"button","text":"поблагодарить и уйти","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":850.4222641999131,"y":-160.8536203050933,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"d2d14f56-0bf8-4ae3-89d6-56640c3280c3","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Изучить","content":{"items":[{"id":"d33a6b43-0834-40d0-96b2-13e5f35fc806","type":"text","text":"Вы расшифровываете символы и понимаете, что они указывают на скрытый вход в город. \nОднако путь туда опасен.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"da35d1e5-d5de-4281-963f-577bf393197a","type":"button","text":"пойти по указанному пути","targetNodeId":"990edc55-65d9-42aa-8f71-bad4926dda5b","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4b78011f-96b8-4a77-8f5d-09607b8d7460","type":"button","text":"вернуться в лагерь","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-646.3853094690887,"y":190.2245174771364,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"4bc1f724-adcf-46f8-a56d-4b4151165456","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Продолжить путь","content":{"items":[{"id":"69ea6872-7585-4e14-b913-f1e2917b2f6d","type":"text","text":"Вы продолжаете путь и сталкиваетесь с опасными хищниками. \nВам нужно быстро принять решение.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3300a96c-103a-4e95-b65a-5c59ee756678","type":"button","text":"сразиться с хищниками","targetNodeId":"33236fb1-8a64-4d8a-b7fe-d11a96a8194a","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"c30fc1aa-56fa-4b36-98c2-8b1b7eb916da","type":"button","text":"попытаться спрятаться","targetNodeId":"b5d08cc9-2353-4a10-a3b4-e34d7425bdeb","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-630.5927287474963,"y":-329.60541344047255,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"6904963d-ba72-4e04-8f7f-95b2c5899d4c","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Взять карту","content":{"items":[{"id":"dc8dc3de-e95c-4389-9b61-ecbf09f4c7c5","type":"text","text":"Вы берете карту и видите, что она указывает на скрытый вход в город.\nОднако путь туда опасен.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b44d6312-3e12-4fe3-a454-54c5ab3a003c","type":"button","text":"вернуться назад","targetNodeId":"6098d8c9-95f5-4283-a29b-cde1081738aa","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4970b76b-21c3-4c99-a486-9f54bc352712","type":"button","text":"пойти по указанному пути","targetNodeId":"990edc55-65d9-42aa-8f71-bad4926dda5b","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":205.03747297372047,"y":595.5790602708473,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"48d780f2-18aa-4b0e-aed6-10ae2072d52d","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Попросить проводника","content":{"items":[{"id":"2e2fe827-b8c0-4e24-bbe1-b3be49d4818d","type":"text","text":"Один из местных соглашается стать вашим проводником. \nОн ведет вас к древнему храму, где, по его словам, находится вход в город.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"5cfade15-486c-4cf9-aead-4906281507b8","type":"button","text":"зайти в храм","targetNodeId":"40c3cd03-a447-49d8-a6de-0879b1658a12","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":739.4180096547869,"y":72.04381220171531,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"990edc55-65d9-42aa-8f71-bad4926dda5b","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Пойти по указанному пути","content":{"items":[{"id":"7c50c33b-d447-4f8b-902e-01e80e2b449e","type":"text","text":"Вы следуете по пути и находите древний храм. \nВнутри вы видите статую с загадочными символами.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"31c5311e-2270-45b1-b437-1d3cf2d79958","type":"button","text":"изучить статую","targetNodeId":"0efd8a7a-8cd0-44d9-b677-b70332eb11f5","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4e6af1f1-e54a-40d1-bc51-1f05e3b71d66","type":"button","text":"вернуться","targetNodeId":"b6f42c10-cf03-45ea-9061-3b99e4b1c3f0","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-645.7449153701282,"y":391.99570287327043,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"0efd8a7a-8cd0-44d9-b677-b70332eb11f5","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"статуя","content":{"items":[{"id":"55125c66-2e3f-4f1e-b20f-5f7043cc4888","type":"text","text":"Вы замечаете, что символы на статуе совпадают с теми, что вы видели на камне в джунглях. \nВы нажимаете на символы в определенном порядке, и пол под вами начинает двигаться.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3f085b05-8ee9-4f85-b996-cff8b28e5b4f","type":"button","text":"спуститься вниз","targetNodeId":"dee8bf02-3faf-474a-848a-aaa61e9a8871","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"41c363d1-b41f-4fb5-8efe-1b192d26c91a","type":"button","text":"остаться на месте","targetNodeId":"42f87f0a-9dc7-432e-b394-2819c06139de","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-644.9163623581067,"y":580.8629608855364,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"dee8bf02-3faf-474a-848a-aaa61e9a8871","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"спуск вниз","content":{"items":[{"id":"4b496614-01cc-41d2-af99-7b3f73f4a069","type":"text","text":"Вы оказываетесь в подземном туннеле. Впереди виднеется свет. \nВы идете на него и находите огромный зал с древними фресками.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"9e036a05-fa60-4fba-80c7-75d4cec333f7","type":"button","text":"изучить фрески","targetNodeId":"de958379-dce5-4b04-ab46-b643dce780af","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"7ffcd47a-b267-4ae9-b0c7-172662787856","type":"button","text":"продолжить путь","targetNodeId":"54c28d44-b8e9-480c-be7a-ad61672ad829","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1054.5467778305922,"y":610.6390666417553,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"42f87f0a-9dc7-432e-b394-2819c06139de","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"на месте","content":{"items":[{"id":"b6579b92-f890-494e-ac73-0d0f2484f685","type":"text","text":"Вы решаете не рисковать и остаетесь на месте. \nВнезапно пол под вами начинает медленно опускаться, и вы оказываетесь в секретной комнате, заполненной древними артефактами и записями.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e90960c1-1b81-4e25-b613-ea0becb7555a","type":"button","text":"исследовать комнату","targetNodeId":"0147de03-a421-4479-b53d-8db5d477776e","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"1cd92d5a-7207-490e-a304-7e157f26996e","type":"button","text":"попытаться вернуться","targetNodeId":"4545fc18-ae9e-47b8-8431-e26e7daba207","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-488.50221763871366,"y":765.2218898970783,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"de958379-dce5-4b04-ab46-b643dce780af","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"изучить фрески","content":{"items":[{"id":"25c8c77b-b595-44cd-b87e-fcdf5a4e5dad","type":"text","text":"Фрески рассказывают историю Затерянного Города. \nВы узнаете, что город был уничтожен из-за жадности его жителей. В конце зала вы видите дверь с загадочным замком.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"c4e8f318-21e6-47c8-8403-c6f01f86e0f4","type":"button","text":"вернуться","targetNodeId":"dee8bf02-3faf-474a-848a-aaa61e9a8871","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"c2448617-e14c-4822-af28-ca26fad77d28","type":"button","text":"попытаться открыть дверь","targetNodeId":"19fdc699-d405-4830-99c7-fba218aa0292","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1055.7878820219562,"y":860.6491012722677,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"0147de03-a421-4479-b53d-8db5d477776e","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Исследовать комнату","content":{"items":[{"id":"2fb9c854-f259-4a90-a82c-ca7e0852f774","type":"text","text":"Вы находите древние свитки, которые рассказывают о том, как город был уничтожен из-за жадности его правителей. Среди артефактов вы замечаете странный механизм, похожий на портал.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e94d7541-f114-4d4b-b719-a488e1260561","type":"button","text":"активировать механизм","targetNodeId":"f17ad092-1179-4718-b557-b3ef1367e031","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b26c5dec-62e3-47f6-9793-7ef6ab6805d7","type":"button","text":"взять свитки и уйти","targetNodeId":"072db584-a72c-49a3-8305-7e2fdd68960a","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-487.5622756493933,"y":1103.6606939653173,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"54c28d44-b8e9-480c-be7a-ad61672ad829","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Обвал","content":{"items":[{"id":"17703336-5684-435e-9a0d-1af8aaa6306b","type":"text","text":"Как только вы углубились в длинный коридор, случился обвал.\nВы остались живы, но пути назад и вперёд полностью завалены.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"30c8bcd5-3033-464a-8f54-ab9ccd180685","type":"button","text":"завершить квест","targetNodeId":"65604966-e583-47da-8476-ce41eee231a7","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1239.3151084210529,"y":610.63132054861,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"4545fc18-ae9e-47b8-8431-e26e7daba207","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"попытаться вернуться","content":{"items":[{"id":"3dccccde-5cea-4a46-9a3e-f96954c1e646","type":"text","text":"Вы пытаетесь вернуться, но механизм, который привел вас сюда, больше не работает. \nТеперь вы заперты в этой комнате.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a8405d72-8fa7-48e8-aae7-8685a42b070c","type":"button","text":"искать другой выход","targetNodeId":"78a8278a-a58a-414b-bfed-dab1057dc246","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ef175426-8ce8-4a09-8821-73add0de99c1","type":"button","text":"смириться с судьбой","targetNodeId":"51915d56-581e-4bb6-b00b-c1e5963a9014","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-299.20297832683235,"y":793.488143098519,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"78a8278a-a58a-414b-bfed-dab1057dc246","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"искать другой выход","content":{"items":[{"id":"000ba5b9-ece4-4b12-9cbf-81e68a435c8e","type":"text","text":"Вы находите скрытый проход, который ведет обратно в храм. \nТеперь вы можете продолжить свои поиски.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"fd51c1e6-fd54-4b1b-8f02-de0d05547a1e","type":"button","text":"вернуться в храм","targetNodeId":"40c3cd03-a447-49d8-a6de-0879b1658a12","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-218.63925779160488,"y":992.0652366947138,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"51915d56-581e-4bb6-b00b-c1e5963a9014","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"смириться с судьбой","content":{"items":[{"id":"80078f94-8b16-4200-b53e-aad8b86e56d4","type":"text","text":"Вы смиряетесь с судьбой и проводите остаток жизни в древнем городе, наблюдая за его расцветом и упадком.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e71b7823-5edd-4a29-ad3a-a98fbcbae3ce","type":"button","text":"закончить квест","targetNodeId":"a406e803-06dd-49fc-9957-febe5b653adb","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-216.11379125587496,"y":597.589280402893,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"a406e803-06dd-49fc-9957-febe5b653adb","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Конец (древний город)","content":{"items":[{"id":"e4e9a61e-93fd-49fc-a1fc-d2e1926e1877","type":"text","text":"Похоже это конец! Вы навсегда остались в древнем городе.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"1dac8f77-ea68-4d76-8a5f-f5d92628bc45","type":"button","text":"начать сначала","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-213.67362504226594,"y":423.78355215223,"color":4292030255,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"40c3cd03-a447-49d8-a6de-0879b1658a12","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"путь в храм","content":{"items":[{"id":"0e67f85b-9691-44dd-bd55-8135e6f1e54e","type":"text","text":"Внутри храма вы видите статую с загадочными символами. \nКажется, это ключ к разгадке.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ad0bacf9-127d-4609-8a38-ff8ca7450aae","type":"button","text":"изучить статую","targetNodeId":"0efd8a7a-8cd0-44d9-b677-b70332eb11f5","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-17.0497943352441,"y":1045.0687889981689,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"f17ad092-1179-4718-b557-b3ef1367e031","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"активировать механизм","content":{"items":[{"id":"27490b3f-64be-44f2-844f-d2740cb83a2a","type":"text","text":"Вы активируете механизм, и перед вами открывается портал. \nВы чувствуете, что он ведет в другое измерение или время.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"e4ccc817-d430-4565-b549-e211605ac389","type":"button","text":"войти в портал","targetNodeId":"b2d28572-9754-456c-a7cd-b8e26d48b527","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"34bf6585-b5f2-48ed-804d-7ee6fae015a3","type":"button","text":"остаться и исследовать дальше","targetNodeId":"0147de03-a421-4479-b53d-8db5d477776e","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-626.7514618685068,"y":1347.2338839604824,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"072db584-a72c-49a3-8305-7e2fdd68960a","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"взять свитки и уйти","content":{"items":[{"id":"fcba0e9a-effd-4811-a104-c0e19bb6d20f","type":"text","text":"Вы берете свитки и покидаете комнату. Теперь у вас есть ценные знания, но вы так и не узнали, куда вел механизм.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ed0e4c71-2719-4856-bbce-e4faf7d19619","type":"button","text":"завершить квест","targetNodeId":"c7e86a13-ea40-45fa-b65f-7c5ec514cb2d","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-383.4624294918162,"y":1300.5093995655673,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"b2d28572-9754-456c-a7cd-b8e26d48b527","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"войти в портал","content":{"items":[{"id":"493f7f63-d28e-4e05-86b6-128130cb6f7b","type":"text","text":"Вы входите в портал и оказываетесь в древнем городе, но он выглядит совсем иначе — как будто вы перенеслись в прошлое. \nГород еще не разрушен, и его жители смотрят на вас с удивлением.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"299ca169-4f71-4b4f-b8f2-56cae31327e3","type":"button","text":"объяснить всё жителям","targetNodeId":"10dc1ed5-e510-4717-9971-5f8e43f1e1c1","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"04ab2ed3-557b-4cdf-8a45-b932f954729d","type":"button","text":"скрыться и наблюдать","targetNodeId":"ad8f64ac-dbc0-49ba-824e-a926d33c86dd","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-625.7233756566823,"y":1534.4688985990865,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"10dc1ed5-e510-4717-9971-5f8e43f1e1c1","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"объяснить жителям","content":{"items":[{"id":"c3d175c2-9dcc-4283-9519-abffcdfeda3a","type":"text","text":"Вы пытаетесь объяснить жителям, кто вы и откуда, но они не понимают ваш язык. Внезапно появляются стражники и берут вас под стражу.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"26cffa39-0e6e-4c69-a7bc-f458100d5532","type":"button","text":"попытаться сбежать","targetNodeId":"ba926695-7e10-4210-8500-32dc27017478","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a33f671c-03fb-4b87-973c-bb45f0590766","type":"button","text":"смириться с судьбой","targetNodeId":"51915d56-581e-4bb6-b00b-c1e5963a9014","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-789.7899249164527,"y":1776.9611683705584,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"ad8f64ac-dbc0-49ba-824e-a926d33c86dd","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"скрыться и наблюдать","content":{"items":[{"id":"62f0e53f-a198-49d9-9516-dd3a9218b6dd","type":"text","text":"Вы скрываетесь и наблюдаете за жизнью города. \nСо временем вы понимаете, что можете изменить его судьбу, но решаете не вмешиваться.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"ef864cb9-7bd3-4bc4-8a33-6d713781b519","type":"button","text":"завершить квест","targetNodeId":"a406e803-06dd-49fc-9957-febe5b653adb","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-534.9013852259432,"y":1722.4986378141357,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"ba926695-7e10-4210-8500-32dc27017478","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"сбежать","content":{"items":[{"id":"120eeb53-9ab3-4ba7-b203-792f4e73e653","type":"text","text":"Вам удается сбежать из-под стражи, но теперь вы вынуждены скрываться в городе. Вы решаете найти способ вернуться в свое время.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"80a4cae4-13fd-4e0f-8d5f-6602b75e8079","type":"button","text":"остаться в прошлом","targetNodeId":"2e21015d-e7ee-422d-9789-fd0d8dbd1a51","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"bc109a5c-39fe-48d5-8750-6b86c1c1fb7f","type":"button","text":"искать портал","targetNodeId":"ed67c6aa-e053-4050-ab12-9fdeeca80d40","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-916.4061397107766,"y":1948.9313755143517,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"2e21015d-e7ee-422d-9789-fd0d8dbd1a51","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"в прошлом","content":{"items":[{"id":"5ce32fc2-3441-4646-9904-d1ed4a52c031","type":"text","text":"Вы решаете остаться в прошлом и начать новую жизнь в древнем городе. \nСо временем вы становитесь частью его истории.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"9861ee6e-009e-4531-a404-fb0acb464c20","type":"button","text":"завершить квест","targetNodeId":"a406e803-06dd-49fc-9957-febe5b653adb","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-761.3656072387081,"y":2177.9111462550686,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"ed67c6aa-e053-4050-ab12-9fdeeca80d40","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"искать портал","content":{"items":[{"id":"37672b0b-1a85-444e-ac9e-6d875806bcd2","type":"text","text":"Вы находите древний храм, где, как вам кажется, находится портал. \nОднако, чтобы активировать его, нужно решить загадку.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"45db5a56-7640-46bd-92a4-ecfb8587e173","type":"button","text":"отступить","targetNodeId":"2e21015d-e7ee-422d-9789-fd0d8dbd1a51","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"45b8d249-e394-4c20-96e0-c3a9f9307704","type":"button","text":"решить загадку","targetNodeId":"bac6f1da-5290-4593-b1fd-fe7ec6c8308f","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1054.4275457402073,"y":2176.796813365603,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"bac6f1da-5290-4593-b1fd-fe7ec6c8308f","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"загадка","content":{"items":[{"id":"3332057f-6801-4c19-a46f-1a65fe56dc8e","type":"text","text":"Вы решаете загадку, и портал активируется. Вы возвращаетесь в свое время, но теперь у вас есть знания о прошлом города.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3991f883-a513-4a3e-acaf-cb404c5fc8a5","type":"button","text":"завершить квест","targetNodeId":"7af295cd-af6d-41da-a401-146cbd4aa59d","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1054.3678270911485,"y":2368.3025180090203,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"19fdc699-d405-4830-99c7-fba218aa0292","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"открыть дверь","content":{"items":[{"id":"9d0e1e05-1c86-4e86-b6f7-cbbe5c3f52d3","type":"text","text":"Вы используете знания, полученные из фресок, чтобы открыть дверь. \nОна медленно открывается, и вы видите перед собой Затерянный Город.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a2b4f2d3-b5b2-4934-8489-924b178452f8","type":"button","text":"вернуться","targetNodeId":"de958379-dce5-4b04-ab46-b643dce780af","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"5b4f0678-5b8d-4c93-af35-30c95f4df025","type":"button","text":"войти в город","targetNodeId":"210cee39-755f-4a3a-adf2-ed75fafa6576","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1055.052971693652,"y":1077.6151981639425,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"210cee39-755f-4a3a-adf2-ed75fafa6576","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"войти в город","content":{"items":[{"id":"eb075dc0-6ac6-41af-8fe0-844048e068db","type":"text","text":"Вы оказываетесь в древнем городе. \nВ центре вы видите огромный храм, который, вероятно, хранит главную тайну города.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"47a48308-30aa-4797-9852-67583181407e","type":"button","text":"осмотреть город","targetNodeId":"549a22df-e028-418c-aec1-f01cf06c5c0f","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"2a8a5486-0944-4f98-9f7d-5bf5511215a1","type":"button","text":"исследовать храм","targetNodeId":"85071b0b-f2d1-49fb-8b84-e618fd5ee48d","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1138.8930378485315,"y":1287.2945765021086,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"549a22df-e028-418c-aec1-f01cf06c5c0f","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"осмотреть город","content":{"items":[{"id":"90a9afdc-053e-4d32-a18b-da36f552f658","type":"text","text":"Вы осматриваете город и находите множество древних артефактов. \nОднако, вы понимаете, что город охраняется, и решаете уйти.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"3038e403-fed3-4c90-827b-c872e10d525c","type":"button","text":"завершить квест","targetNodeId":"d3398d36-09b6-473e-9927-1ecff381d8aa","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1138.0947280305154,"y":1477.7744345942413,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"85071b0b-f2d1-49fb-8b84-e618fd5ee48d","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"исследовать храм","content":{"items":[{"id":"27c5b98b-3a50-44f4-8ed9-cbd4100bdc7a","type":"text","text":"Внутри храма вы находите древний артефакт — Кристалл Времени. \nОднако, как только вы берете его, появляются Хранители.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"456afbae-bd85-4689-b9a4-dbd8f5e9336e","type":"button","text":"сразиться с хранителями","targetNodeId":"e2ea2dff-0e8b-490d-9e4a-9c901e2b88a6","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"646fa321-ac4a-48e4-b35b-3f2d16a22712","type":"button","text":"договориться с ними","targetNodeId":"00ec950c-ef4d-4cc4-b224-27aa62b5dd9f","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1326.5428529636697,"y":1326.706177031395,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"e2ea2dff-0e8b-490d-9e4a-9c901e2b88a6","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"сразиться с хранителями","content":{"items":[{"id":"81b67440-4b10-4b3b-9f7c-94c939bb1198","type":"text","text":"Хранители — могущественные противники. Вам нужно использовать все свои навыки, чтобы победить.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4093de65-953f-42e7-8e78-db75e459c550","type":"button","text":"сражаться вручную","targetNodeId":"2e657a7d-0708-45de-83e1-44310a6fac90","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"5372daf5-be3e-4ab6-8ab7-b46000b0c8ad","type":"button","text":"использовать артефакт","targetNodeId":"43768dd0-40ad-4207-b3db-6a8a9620ac74","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1729.9976668453266,"y":1018.7021613859616,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"00ec950c-ef4d-4cc4-b224-27aa62b5dd9f","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"договориться","content":{"items":[{"id":"77314a9e-0f82-4d0c-b333-290b3166b35b","type":"text","text":"Вы пытаетесь договориться с Хранителями, но они не поддаются на уговоры. \nВам приходится отступить.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"d6d0d2ba-253f-4796-b8c1-aeb4b5a15dd1","type":"button","text":"завершить квест","targetNodeId":"7af295cd-af6d-41da-a401-146cbd4aa59d","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1494.9691176868898,"y":1483.0580623121516,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"2e657a7d-0708-45de-83e1-44310a6fac90","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"сразиться вручную","content":{"items":[{"id":"9f7bd800-24b9-4b40-823d-6b81b89a2707","type":"text","text":"Вы сражаетесь с Хранителями, но они слишком сильны. \nВам удается спастись, но артефакт остается в их руках.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4562a398-16b3-4395-8f6b-c78a89740eb6","type":"button","text":"завершить квест","targetNodeId":"7af295cd-af6d-41da-a401-146cbd4aa59d","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1626.1231817172863,"y":807.7949906877495,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"b5d08cc9-2353-4a10-a3b4-e34d7425bdeb","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"спрятаться","content":{"items":[{"id":"c22cdf0e-9ab1-4510-b2ec-58c405aa4a82","type":"text","text":"Вы успешно прячетесь и ждете, пока хищники уйдут. \nПосле этого вы продолжаете путь.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"063d084e-6964-4a6f-8e62-1539940cd6a0","type":"button","text":"продолжить расследование","targetNodeId":"b6f42c10-cf03-45ea-9061-3b99e4b1c3f0","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-512.6992801127025,"y":-517.2656112402451,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"33236fb1-8a64-4d8a-b7fe-d11a96a8194a","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"сразиться с хищниками","content":{"items":[{"id":"f71eb986-3e16-4b0c-99a7-35dfc70d6e7a","type":"text","text":"Вы сражаетесь с хищниками, но силы неравны.\nВам удается спастись, но вы теряете часть снаряжения.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"a5fb8a4d-6abf-4406-9a64-c44226e7e57d","type":"button","text":"вернуться в лагерь","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-795.7575087303632,"y":-525.9001394379966,"color":4280492835,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"43768dd0-40ad-4207-b3db-6a8a9620ac74","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"артефакт","content":{"items":[{"id":"40229c67-30f5-4691-bd42-3b28a5453ad8","type":"text","text":"Вы активируете Кристалл Времени, и Хранители замирают. \nВы успешно покидаете город с артефактом.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"4526aea3-0f1f-4832-8361-59e442ec30d1","type":"button","text":"закончить квест","targetNodeId":"2d294d92-8da1-4602-bc0c-b4863c1473fa","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1889.5282129194572,"y":800.0995239146397,"color":4294278144,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"2d294d92-8da1-4602-bc0c-b4863c1473fa","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"финал","content":{"items":[{"id":"61c286d8-e549-4fb6-a226-2d04897ade76","type":"text","text":"Вы возвращаетесь домой с Кристаллом Времени. \nВаше открытие меняет историю человечества.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"277cf6dd-5492-40a6-a574-8101062c72de","type":"button","text":"начать игру сначала","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1889.4917980563732,"y":516.893221133512,"color":4278221163,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"c7e86a13-ea40-45fa-b65f-7c5ec514cb2d","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Конец (свитки)","content":{"items":[{"id":"41749424-b145-4033-babb-59a0a32540b3","type":"text","text":"Вы приобрели знания, но не нашли древний артефакт. Возможно стоит попробовать ещё раз. ","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"addb12ea-981b-47af-aa6d-5abda1c5eeef","type":"button","text":"начать сначала","targetNodeId":"a406e803-06dd-49fc-9957-febe5b653adb","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-195.11477318066466,"y":1299.7266588596797,"color":4292030255,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"7af295cd-af6d-41da-a401-146cbd4aa59d","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Конец (древний город. знания)","content":{"items":[{"id":"47d7481d-0677-48b1-9685-9af4dfb7213f","type":"text","text":"Вы побывали в древнем городе. Вы много знаете про него, однако вам никто не поверит. Остаётся писать книги и рассказы на тему существования древних городов. ","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"06b55cf4-16e0-44a2-a244-eb0ff15fd248","type":"button","text":"начать сначала","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1053.3141696987345,"y":2558.175663041909,"color":4292030255,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"d3398d36-09b6-473e-9927-1ecff381d8aa","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Конец (артефакты)","content":{"items":[{"id":"354ed1c2-9798-4642-8b15-d7f891536e94","type":"text","text":"Вы повидали древний город, и вынесли из него разные священные артефакты. Но как только вы попытались продать артефакты торговцу, они рассыпались в пыль.","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"b53eccf7-db30-4e3c-90f1-da5b321e591a","type":"button","text":"начать сначала","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-953.6908772530538,"y":1477.9618840710812,"color":4292030255,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"65604966-e583-47da-8476-ce41eee231a7","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Конец (обвал)","content":{"items":[{"id":"e4348c10-f039-4188-8470-829681171d0e","type":"text","text":"Обвал был очень мощным, что завалило любой путь к спасению. Похоже, вам придётся провести остаток дня в этом древнем месте. ","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"6fffe23e-9365-4296-baa3-411d96a77ebc","type":"button","text":"играть сначала","targetNodeId":"956ab20c-ac57-444b-9587-aea770177fb8","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":-1240.042832063757,"y":429.2632061576667,"color":4292030255,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0},{"id":"f7c1f27e-3c82-47f4-8c64-85a6e58c7da0","chapterId":"7be54bd5-7cb0-4a66-9b50-5e75bd0a8f64","title":"Дневник","content":{"items":[{"id":"74de8826-f4ef-4d0a-a5c6-eeecfc055848","type":"text","text":"Моё имя Пол. Я уже несколько дней пытаюсь найти древний город. Пока всё безуспешно. Местные жители говорят, что там есть какой-то очень ценный артефакт. Все чёрные копатели и археологи пытаются его найти.\nЯ должен первым попасть в этот город.\nСегодня я снова попробую отыскать туда вход. Это будет не просто, но я попробую... ","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0},{"id":"21415143-6815-46ac-9cd8-cf00ac257c92","type":"button","text":"назад","targetNodeId":"6098d8c9-95f5-4283-a29b-cde1081738aa","flex":1,"crossAxisAlignment":"center","rowTextAlignment":"center","isHidden":false,"textFit":"auto","wrapText":true,"volume":1.0}]},"x":501.18770688109345,"y":-205.61181726651054,"color":4278238420,"backgroundAudioVolume":1.0}],"groups":[],"comments":[]}